供詞<br />\n<br />\n法庭接納辯方對PW1受襲過程的質疑：PW1在庭上作供指稱被告使用雨傘插中PW1，唯書面證供只提及被擊中，裁判官明白事件發生在電光火石間，但認為插中以及擊中是兩個不同的動作，證供可信性成疑<br />\n<br />\n加上PW1供稱被告人推撞他的事情並沒有片段支持，控方未能證明襲擊前有何身體接觸。而PW1正在追截黑衣人，理應不會與被告人發生衝突，法庭不能排除被告的自辯<br />\n<br />\n法庭裁定被告人罪名不成立<br />\n<br />\n裁判官批准訟費申請"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T08:22:54.000Z","msg":"插中同擊中成為關鍵字眼<br />\n所以手足們記得<br />\n無律師在場一定一定一定要無野講<br />\n就算啲狗點威迫利誘<br />\n無律師就乜撚都唔好講<br />\n記得啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd26fd71da262cfd91fc845a185a3ad9071b59b","tid":2130351,"uid":14739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"055d7ce2ad9f468c96c26a98d08870f89b16854f","tid":2130351,"uid":2054,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"bacefa9ca4b6e0250065cded61190d131eb5edcd","tid":2130351,"uid":36049,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:15:37.000Z","msg":"Sanction真係好能尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:16:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.commondreams.org/sites/default/files/styles/cd_large/public/headlines/pompeo_5.jpg?itok=zIi_zc6e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.commondreams.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fcd_large%2Fpublic%2Fheadlines%2Fpompeo_5.jpg%3Fitok%3DzIi_zc6e&h=65e4b1aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T08:24:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70d8f147d0b282f264ff64114718f8c4132606ee","tid":2130351,"uid":230104,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"00fb7405bdc28db480113aba6bc05804ad83964d","tid":2130351,"uid":132587,"like":137,"dislike":3,"score":134,"citedBy":2,"r