lyTime":"2020-07-29T08:24:27.000Z","msg":"朱西迪阻頭阻勢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T08:33:04.000Z","msg":"四眼哥哥.jpg"},{"pid":"a33f69154457e62e8fa82c136ad3184f18b5af9d","tid":2130351,"uid":76314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T08:45:52.000Z","msg":"制裁近了"},{"pid":"4588b0023d2b85c603dd8cb2ede0dd60fb1a3670","tid":2130351,"uid":185424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T08:53:07.000Z","msg":"好人一世平安"},{"pid":"6102444c3b6d69c1e1e8634f0d45a2feb9e41449","tid":2130351,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:02:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278b93130fbc4d0bf65b67d9034e5da8c3729189","tid":2130351,"uid":19640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:12:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b98672f1554e722a7f0632cff87cec2ae8803a5f","tid":2130351,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:16:47.000Z","msg":"裁判官指遇襲警長的供詞不可靠，控方亦未能舉證說明事件的完整過程，因而裁定被告的襲警罪名不成立。法庭另准辯方申請逾3萬港元訟費。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，22歲被告蔡浩民於去年7月14日，在沙田新城市廣場襲擊正在執行職務的警務人員。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官裁決時指，控方說法是警長在追截黑衣人時，突然遭被告以雨傘襲擊。警長擋開被告攻擊後，被告再持兩傘與他對峙；辯方說法則是被告與友人失散後，突然被人從後叉頸及推撞，才會舉起雨傘作自衞。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官表示，本案關鍵是警長證供的可靠性，惟他在作供時的未能清楚描述襲擊過程，在重要環節的說法有差異，故其供詞受質疑，法庭未能依賴。裁判官又指，警長不會無緣無故接觸被告，惟控方呈堂的影片沒有拍到事件的完整過程，不足以支持控方說法，遂裁定被告無罪。"},{"pid":"4dc9bdfd59a6599f4f421fb42a758728418c362a","tid":2130351,"uid":195690,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"00fb7405bdc28db480113aba6bc05804ad83964d","tid":2130351,"uid":132587,"like":137,"dislike":3,"score":134,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:08:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:22:52.000Z","msg":"睇到好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不斷loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b7de6da2c99c2b61544599946d17199a84cf5a","tid":2130351,"uid":95777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4c5bda9fc2e3e073275099e1d4576d1ac6f4baf","tid":2130351,"uid":69416,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"bacefa9ca4b6e0250065cded61190d131eb5edcd","tid":2130351,"uid":36049,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:15:37.000Z","msg":"Sanction真係好能尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:26:17.000Z","msg":"隔離蘇文隆無撚驚過<br />\n車尾箱放辣椒油同棒球棍判18個月"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:25:47.000Z","msg":"件垃圾蘇含開共撚架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係街度唔知會唔會見到佢呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a934a2c5ab58e143f7ebe32a47ed3f28f888174","tid":2130351,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:29:30.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"fec274c29236c5740c5dc6d2dac79e11f70c89c9","tid":2130351,"uid":240362,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:47:58.000Z","msg":"UPDATE: 法庭裁定錄影片段屬於事後後段的情況，片段屬中性，可以支持控辯雙方案情，在缺乏其他證據的情況下，控方案情只能依賴PW1的供詞<br />\n<br />\n法庭接納辯方對PW1受襲過程的質疑：PW1在庭上作供指稱被告使用雨傘插中PW1，唯書面證供只提及被擊中，裁判官明白事件發生在電光火石間，但認為插中以及擊中是兩個不同的動作，證供可信性成疑<br />\n<br />\n加上PW1供稱被告人推撞他的事情並沒有片段支持，控方未能證明襲擊前有何身體接觸。而PW1正在追截黑衣人，理應不會與被告人發生衝突，法庭不能排除被告的自辯<br />\n<br />\n法庭裁定被告人罪名不成立<br />\n<br />\n裁判官批准訟費申請"}}